ENGINEERING DRAWING SPECIFICATION & CAD METADATA — PUMP P-401
Drawing Ref: DWG-P401-LAYOUT-001 | Sheet 1 of 3 | Scale 1:10 | Format: DWG/DXF
Asset Association: Centrifugal Pump P-401 (Plant A)

1. MECHANICAL SCHEMATIC NOTES
- Suction Flange: 6-inch ANSI Class 150 RF Flange.
- Discharge Flange: 4-inch ANSI Class 150 RF Flange.
- Shaft Diameter: 42 mm (+0.000 / -0.012 mm ground finish).
- Mechanical Seal Chamber: Conforms to API 682 4th Edition, Category 2, Type A arrangement 1.
- Flush Piping: API Plan 11 (Discharge through orifice to seal chamber) & Plan 52 (Unpressurized buffer fluid reservoir).

2. MOUNTING & FOUNDATION
- Baseplate: Heavy-duty cast iron drip-rim baseplate secured with four 24mm anchor bolts.
- Grout Specification: Non-shrink epoxy grout (MasterFlow 648) 50mm thickness.